    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six with crisp throttle response via factory ITBs. This chassis remains rigid, having undergone proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The drivetrain is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a 3.62 limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Suspension is upgraded with Bilstein coilovers, providing adjustable damping and improved roll center geometry. The VANOS system has been recently overhauled to ensure timing precision and torque consistency. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
