      "description": "This 2018 executive sedan strikes the perfect balance between performance and value. Finished in a sophisticated Metallic Graphite, the exterior maintains a deep gloss, though it shows minor signs of careful use such as small stone chips on the front bumper and a tiny scuff on the rear passenger wheel, consistent with regular commuting. Inside, the premium leather upholstery is in great shape with no rips or stains, and the cabin remains smoke-free. Every electronic feature, from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this vehicle has been consistently maintained, with a complete service log and a brand-new set of all-season tires recently installed. It drives smooth and quiet, offering a refined experience for its next owner. This is an honest, dependable car that has been well-looked after, making it a fantastic choice for anyone seeking luxury and reliability.",
